definition: "roof" radical in Chinese characters (Kangxi radical 40), occurring in 家, 定, 安 etc/see also 寶蓋|宝盖[bao3 gai4]
other/the others/else/other than it/in addition to the thing mentioned above
variant of 維他命|维他命[wei2 ta1 ming4]

sentences.english: It takes away our edge, makes us groggy, and disrupts our sleep.
sentences.chinese: 它讓我們反應遲鈍，頭昏腦脹，擾亂我們的睡眠。

sentences.english: It was the site of a British victory over the Saxons in571. Population, 74, 500.
sentences.chinese: 它是571年大不列顛人打敗撒克遜人的遺址。

sentences.english: It's got a new government, you know, which hasn't governed before.
sentences.chinese: 它剛換了政府，一個從未執政過的新政府。

sentences.english: The book was out of print, but I eventually ran it to earth at a secondhand bookshop.
sentences.chinese: 那本書已經絕版，但我終於在一家舊書店淘到了它。

sentences.english: It adds a new entry to the first line in a file.
sentences.chinese: 它在文件的首行添加一個新條目。

sentences.english: Lemons contain pectin fiber, which assists in fighting hunger cravings.
sentences.chinese: 檸檬富含果膠纖維，它又可以抵抗飢餓。

sentences.english: It doesn't have a point. It's all process and form.
sentences.chinese: 它沒有目的，而僅僅是過程和形式。

sentences.english: It is now in flyable storage in Fort Worth.
sentences.chinese: 它現在在封存在沃斯堡。

sentences.english: So it's a kind of machine which take advantage of fatigue-fracture.
sentences.chinese: 因而，它是一種化害爲利，利用疲勞斷裂下料的機械。

sentences.english: He was always excited by his life and busy with where it was going.
sentences.chinese: 他總是爲他的生活而興奮，忙着它要去的地方。

sentences.english: Vernet glanced at the key but made no move to touch it.
sentences.chinese: 韋爾內看了一眼那把鑰匙，卻沒有去動它。

sentences.english: Here is a list of what it will include.
sentences.chinese: 以下是它所能夠包含的新特性列表。

sentences.english: Happy is a bird, it found only in fulfillment of the tree.
sentences.chinese: 快樂的是一隻鳥，它只棲息在花繁葉茂的樹上。

sentences.english: It's not going to happen overnight.
It has peculiar character comparing with other interferometers.
sentences.chinese: 與其它干涉儀相比，具有獨特的優點。

sentences.english: Eco-fashion has certainly proved that it has enough caché in the fashion world.
sentences.chinese: 生態時裝還證明它在時尚界有着足夠的影響力。
